insert into wa_template (template_id, name, category, body, buttons, usage_count) values (30738, 'debt_review_advice_tmpl', 'advice', 'Unfortunately, banks cannot legally approve new vehicle finance while under debt review. ⛔

Nobody can remove debt review unless all accounts are fully settled. Avoid scams, and do not apply for new credit, as it damages your profile.

Once you receive your Clearance Certificate, we can apply! How to prepare:
✅ Settle accounts to start your credit fresh.
✅ Build a paying credit profile for 3 to 6 months.
✅ Aim for a 610 credit score (ClearScore).
✅ Keep credit utilization under 50% (e.g., R5k on a R10k limit).
✅ Always pay more than the minimum installment.
✅ Cellphone and gym contracts do not build vehicle credibility.
❌ IMPORTANT: Do not make any credit applications.

I am saving your number to share helpful advice and vehicle specials on my Status. 🙏

Please save mine. Remember: Lumina Auto offers a R5000 referral fee directly to YOU for each successful referral! 🤝', '[]'::jsonb, 7);
